items.title: GM recalls more than 23,000 Corvettes over fuel leak issue linked to fires
items.description: General Motors has recalled more than 23,000 Chevrolet Corvettes in response to a fuel leak issue connected to multiple reported fires.

items.title: Southwest rolls out new conditions for plus-size passenger refunds
items.description: Plus-size travelers must buy extra seats on Southwest flights with assigned seating, with refunds only available if flights depart with open seats.

items.title: European, Asian postal services to halt shipments to US after end of de minimis tariff exemption
items.description: Postal services across Europe and Asia have paused U.S. deliveries ahead of new Trump administration tariff rules taking effect next Friday, Aug. 29.
